佢如果想自己開（舖）咪早啲決定自己嚟香港開，仲執着材料、個名嘅問題，冇意思啦！」他強調現時的材料包裝顯示「台灣製造」，又指台灣幸福堂「嘈埋呢啲嘢冇意思，細路仔咁！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呃咗個牌頭黎用就亂咁黎<br />\n你無人地個名宣傳撚有咁好生意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9cc38731c1c1d6cbd9bb7d0079400d387a34e4","tid":965304,"uid":65530,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:25:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e54a09f3d76a497b89a84fd5ee4ed863d98e39ed","tid":965304,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"開店數月，何先生指現時生意理想<br />\n係好好生意好多人排. <br />\n<br />\n東喜茶 7,8 點都無人買. 租又貴, 最後收咗皮. <br />\n收皮前半價 , <br />\n目的係清咗食材.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2f24c693c285cfbb9a03f15b428c30d83879b0","tid":965304,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:41:10.000Z","msg":"對面 share tea 都賣到 30蚊杯 企硬呢個價.<br />\n 人地寧願去幸福堂."},{"pid":"2dcc23de9626017e2cf6289860dcb69616e58655","tid":965304,"uid":35430,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"何生陳生都係典型華表示賤種基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你做代理係攞人地個名開舖呀<br />\n執著？唔好彩？唔介意你畀本支票簿我寫吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f77509197c3c7cb73af66f9afb4746cea01adb","tid":965304,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何生陳生都係典型華人賤種基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你做代理係攞人地個名開舖呀<br />\n執著？唔好彩？唔介意你畀本支票簿我寫吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"